57E].mkv<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://nyaa.si/view/1099880\">https://nyaa.si/view/1099880</a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"691","username":"madrid2011","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"691","dbdateline":"1544053278","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41844659","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-12-6 07:43","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41844648&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">madrid2011 发表于 2018-12-6 07:41</font></a><br />\r\n英文熟肉現在才出爐.....</div><br />\n比预期的两周要快嘛<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"692","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"692","dbdateline":"1544053422","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41844753","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"n.dante","authorid":"113110","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:00","message":"我觉得这部电影真的想描绘的是多数友情都带有的一个现实条件，那就是两个人需要处在对等的位置。所以当她们两个都在追求同一件事情时，现实的差距让她们永远没办法站到一起，这是一种巨大的压力，让落后的那一方不断的陷入自我矛盾。当最后希美放弃了音乐梦想时，她才终于释然了，能够坦然得和霙相处。这并不是什么关于独占欲之类的，关于励志之类的，关于同性爱之类的东西。而是更加残酷却因而更加美丽的东西。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我觉得看到山田尚子这部电影能表现这种精确的感情已经超越很多上面那位吹的不知道哪里的“文艺电影”了。至于全片的镜头符号解读都是次要的了。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"693","username":"n.dante","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"693","dbdateline":"1544054436","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41844764","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:02","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">djlain 发表于 2018-12-6 02:55</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">不认为文艺片爱好者会是这个片的目标观众，整部片镜头真的太不文艺……过多强调细节之局部镜头的蒙太奇，生 ...</font></div><br />\n我觉得是你对文艺片的想法有问题<br />\r\n文艺片是什么，这是没办法准确定义的<br />\r\n每个导演都有自己特殊的风格，所以这个世界上只存在“某某导演风格的文艺片”，或者也可以说“某部电影有文艺片的风格”<br />\r\n甚至，即使同一个导演，他拍的每一部电影，都有独特的，区别于其他电影的部分<br />\r\n而标准的文艺片是几乎不存在的，因为艺术不是物理学<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而且也不必拘泥于这是不是文艺片，强行把自己放在一个框框里<br />\r\n这就是山田尚子的电影<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"694","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"694","dbdateline":"1544054532","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41844777","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"ゴロー","authorid":"489986","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:04","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41844648&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">madrid2011 发表于 2018-12-6 07:41</font></a><br />\r\n英文熟肉現在才出爐.....</div><br />\n不是说国内的粳米还在上映的时候就多刷把字幕文件做出来了吗","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"695","username":"ゴロー","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"695","dbdateline":"1544054682","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41844793","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:07","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">n.dante 发表于 2018-12-6 07:21</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">她们的故事，对一个凡人来说真的太残酷了。这根本不是什么之前说的精神色情片也不是百合片。她们两个的感情 ...</font></div><br />\n我昨天还在想，如果把希美换成男人，这片好像也成立<br />\r\n然后看到场刊里监督说，把两个女主都换成男人也没问题哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，这电影讲的故事其实与性别是无关的<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"696","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"696","dbdateline":"1544054843","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41844799","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:08","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41844777&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">ゴロー 发表于 2018-12-6 08:04</font></a><br />\r\n不是说国内的粳米还在上映的时候就多刷把字幕文件做出来了吗</div><br />\n没，flankoi没去录音，只是把台词背了下来<br />\r<br />\r<br />\r<div class=\"reply_wrap\">我没录音，我是去电影院刷了12次背下来然后回家写的稿子。主要也是因为自己坐轮椅区结束后会有工作人员来关照，没那胆子录。</div>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"697","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"697","dbdateline":"1544054895","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41844813","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:10","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">xwr 发表于 2018-12-6 07:43</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">比预期的两周要快嘛</font></div><br />\n所以鬼佬已经很肝了嘛","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"698","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"698","dbdateline":"1544055036","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41844818","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"n.dante","authorid":"113110","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:11","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41844793&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">凛凛233 发表于 2018-12-6 08:07</font></a><br />\r\n我昨天还在想，如果把希美换成男人，这片好像也成立<br />\r\n然后看到场刊里监督说，把两个女主都换成男人也没问 ...</div><br />\n至少我是这么认为的。我想说的都在后面的回复里说了。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"699","username":"n.dante","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"699","dbdateline":"1544055086","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41844830","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"古明地雷","authorid":"200891","dateline":"2018-12-6 08:14","message":"希望她们的步调能有一直保持一致的那一天<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/152.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"700","username":"古明地雷","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"700","dbdateline":"1544055277","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41845009","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"John.Zz.Li","authorid":"40