着s1，总共才回了70个帖<br />\r\n这看起来，就像是<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n当然也不能确定就是谁谁马甲/小号/什么的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然后说另外一件事，专楼里就会出现一些奇怪的人，看起来就像是“粪海狂蛆”的样子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以，我经常在想，s1明明是个有趣的地方，有很多聪明人，或者说婆度很高。然而为什么有那么多人恨s1呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我就想起了，还是宝石之国在播的那段时间，论坛人气相对不太行，经常有人发帖问“漫区是不是药丸啊，为什么会这样”诸如此类的问题<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n恰巧这时吧，宝石之国专楼里混进了一只未来导航，胡搅蛮缠了很长时间，恶心的我们不要不要的<br />\r\n某很喜欢宝石之国的人就很气，说“你们整天说s1没人，说业界药丸，现在有好动画了，也有人讨论了，还要被神经病怼，漫区里有这么多SB神经病在，怎么会有人气”<br />\r\n诸如此类的话，原话记不清楚了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n说这话的id已经很久没见到了","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"704","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"704","dbdateline":"1544057957","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41845339","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"Chien","authorid":"494568","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:06","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">wuaistage1 发表于 2018-12-6 02:17</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">这不是明示也不是暗示，这就是</font></div><br />\n有恋无爱吧，最后的告白没有爱情的心跳啊，反而是释然。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"705","username":"Chien","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"705","dbdateline":"1544058376","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41845345","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"amulelernen","authorid":"449184","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:06","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41845199&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">绮陌 发表于 2018-12-6 08:53</font></a><br />\r\n不错不错，我京刻画这种“普通人对身边拥有（自己羡慕而不可得的）天赋的朋友意难平”情绪的功力，当年在冰 ...</div><br />\n其实你把十文字那两男的放到这个故事里说不定也没啥违和感<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/037.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"706","username":"amulelernen","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"706","dbdateline":"1544058402","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41845422","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"chaucerling","authorid":"386142","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:12","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41845345&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">amulelernen 发表于 2018-12-6 09:06</font></a><br />\n其实你把十文字那两男的放到这个故事里说不定也没啥违和感</div><br />\n福部和折木追求的是君子之交，和爱完全不靠边","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"707","username":"chaucerling","adminid":"0","groupid":"52","memberstatus":"0","number":"707","dbdateline":"1544058774","groupiconid":"10"},{"pid":"41845467","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"小白吃不明","authorid":"481845","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:16","message":"卤蛋妹和希美那场戏就是两个自来熟碰到了一起嘛，希美火速就开始直接叫名字了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" /><br />\r\n事实证明自来熟才能打破霙这种人的心防（","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"708","username":"小白吃不明","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"708","dbdateline":"1544058976","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41845507","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"xtwx1716","authorid":"438553","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:18","message":"因为主要人物都是女性，所以这片才能做成这个调调。对于一部弱情节重气氛的电影来说，这个很重要。 以当前这两位的年龄和状态，的确很难去定性这感情性质和成分，但是这种少女之间暧昧的情愫，也是这片着力表现的一个元素。说换性别也成立？我觉得差的有点多。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"709","username":"xtwx1716","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"709","dbdateline":"1544059136","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41845541","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"rei402","authorid":"180721","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:21","message":"长笛反光射到单簧管<br />\r\n观众眼里看到的就是一片嘴唇亲吻了整个身体<br />\r\n精神黄片还真的不是吹的<br />\r\n太色情了<br />\r\n剥离了肉体，纯精神性的高潮<br />\r\n太多细腻的部分了 可怕","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"710","username":"rei402","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"710","dbdateline":"1544059275","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41845566","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"MikiyaKokutou","authorid":"448629","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:23","message":"有意思的是，影片结束两人第一次走出箱庭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n走出箱庭在这里应该有很多层含义，比如二人关系变为joint成功破局、二人皆摆脱束缚展翅翱翔，以及二人的青春即将画上句号。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最后一点还有些伤感啊。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"711","username":"MikiyaKokutou","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"711","dbdateline":"1544059433","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41845633","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"osore","authorid":"184969","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:28","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41844267&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">adonai 发表于 2018-12-6 03:45</font></a><br />\r\n这些信息没看过，我的脑海中完全没有有关希美初中的任何信息<br />\r\n初中做过部长可以这么解释，这是个成 ...</div><br />\n关于希美回归的原因<br />\r\n原作小说里有讲到夏纪和希美聊天的时候，说她大学不准备进吹奏部了，可能随便进个乐团玩玩，这三年吹得太累了<br />\r\n希美表示一定程度上能够理解，平时枯燥的练习只为正式比赛的短短几分钟，但她很享受这种感觉（具体感想我记不得，大概这意思，反正我不理解）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n退部这个事情很正常的，就类似于职场新人觉得所在的公司沙雕/沙雕太多待得不爽，所以就辞职了，不要太常见。谁也不欠谁的<br />\r\n个人觉得明日香是嫉妒希美的，明日香因为母亲的关系不得不背负很多东西，母亲肯定要求她做个“好学生”，所以她不得不拿好学生作为母亲允许她坚持吹奏的筹码。吹奏部也只是作为她能够自己好好吹的一个容身之处，通过参加吹奏部来向母亲证明她不是玩票的性质而是正经搞音乐<br />\r\n明日香能忍猪队友，一方面是她已经被母亲给“锻炼”出来了（从母亲当着老师的面抽她大耳括子后两人的反应可以看出母亲对她动手是家常便饭了），另一方面是她因为家庭的关系不得不背负很多东西，所以想不背也不行，想退也没法退。这也使得她不得不早早变得“成熟”，她平时行为模式的反差感我觉得也是一种消解压力的方式<br />\r\n所以希美想回归时她肯定不爽的，凭什么老娘要忍猪队友两年，当年劝你留你不听，现在你想来就来想走就走？凭什么就你能逍遥自在！<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"712","username":"osore","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"712","dbdateline":"1544059709","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41845637","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"xtwx1716","authorid":"438553","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:28","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">MikiyaKokutou 发表于 2018-12-6 09:23</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">有意思的是，影片结束两人第一次走出箱庭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n走出箱庭在这里应该有很多层含义，比如二人关系变为joint成功 ...</font></div><br />\n影片开始，两人步入鸟笼（校园），坐正，打标题，disjoint，影片开始。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片进程中间只有校内的镜头。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n游泳、联谊，校外的事提到数次，全部略过，一个镜头也没有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n问题解决，两人走出校园（鸟笼），joint，影片结束。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"713","username":"xtwx1716","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"713","dbdateline":"1544059727","groupiconid":"11"},{"pid":"41845761","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"ziyo","authorid":"433163","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:36","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41844092&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">堆雪若叶 发表于 2018-12-6 02:24</font></a><br />\n 数学课确实很有意思，直接看正片的时候看到上课提到质数也是挺意外的（虽然黑板上好像是在讲同余？），但 ...</div><br />\n所以说有人看不懂觉得细节零碎，怀疑监督水平问题，其实是自己观影水平问题<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/039.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"714","username":"ziyo","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"714","dbdateline":"1544060208","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41845854","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"smishe","authorid":"223184","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:43","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41844172&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">djlain 发表于 2018-12-6 02:55</font></a><br />\n不认为文艺片爱好者会是这个片的目标观众，整部片镜头真的太不文艺……过多强调细节之局部镜头的蒙太奇，生 ...</div><br />\n同感，紫罗兰永恒花园这个问题就尤为严重，没想到山田也被稍微传染了一点。","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"715","username":"smishe","adminid":"0","groupid":"49","memberstatus":"0","number":"715","dbdateline":"1544060607","groupiconid":"9"},{"pid":"41845980","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"未来起航","authorid":"467117","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:52","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41845507&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">xtwx1716 发表于 2018-12-06 09:18:56</font></a><br />\n因为主要人物都是女性，所以这片才能做成这个调调。对于一部弱情节重气氛的电影来说，这个很重要。 以当前 ...</div>其实吧……misore我闻出股自闭阿宅味儿……所以性别就这么被略去了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/fi/app/saraba1st/id1221237470?mt=8\"><font color=\"#999999\">-- 来自 能搜索的 Stage1官方 iOS客户端</font></a>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"716","username":"未来起航","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"716","dbdateline":"1544061169","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41846037","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-6 09:56","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">xtwx1716 发表于 2018-12-6 09:18</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">因为主要人物都是女性，所以这片才能做成这个调调。对于一部弱情节重气氛的电影来说，这个很重要。 以当前 ...</font></div><br />\n是监督自己说的啊，前两页有场刊的翻译，你可以看看，挺有意思的","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"717","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"717","dbdateline":"1544061370","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41846116","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"碎片整理","authorid":"480351","dateline":"2018-12-6 10:01","message":"利兹与青鸟这个故事本身看起来很简单，就是爱的放手。由此观点看主角二人，就显得电影波澜不惊，不由得产生“两句话说清楚的事扯这么多有意思？”的疑问。<br />\r\n然而跟着剧情展开，两人的感情层层铺展，“利兹”与“青鸟”二人身份的曝光、反转、融合，直到一句“我喜欢你的双簧管”，如大锤把我既定的思路敲地支离破碎，但又如打开了天窗让人豁然开朗，看到了全新的天地。<br />\r\n从主角二人的爱与妒回看利兹与青鸟，二者之间存在的当真只有爱吗？不尽然，利兹是孤独的，困于一地的，岂能不羡艳嫉妒拥有整个蓝天的青鸟？那么她为何要放开青鸟？只是为了爱吗？也不尽然，当青鸟展翅的那一刻，带走的不仅有利兹的爱，更有她那一份永远无法实现的遨游四海，肆意飞翔的梦。<br />\r\n如此这般，回头再看那一句“我会继续吹双簧管的”，就不再是轻飘飘的称述，而是背负着“利兹”不可能达成却又无法放弃之梦的誓言，在这一刻，两人之间已然建立起了千山万水也无法隔断的牵连。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以说，人家都这样宣誓了，最后那一转头，肯定是要给一个深情的爱之吻的吧？<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/025.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"718","username":"碎片整理","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"718","dbdateline":"1544061701","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41846138","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"凛凛233","authorid":"459764","dateline":"2018-12-6 10:02","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">xtwx1716 发表于 2018-12-6 09:28</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">影片开始，两人步入鸟笼（校园），坐正，打标题，disjoint，影片开始。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片进程中间只有校内的镜头。<br />\r\n</font></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n确实是这样，而且希美回忆起邀请瑛入部之后，有个大约28秒的两只鸟一起翱翔的画面<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n这时候已经不是青鸟了，因为青鸟的故事已经结束了，两个人都解脱获得了自由，现在开始是新的故事了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n前面一直在讲瑛与希美，同时也是丽兹与青鸟的故事，两个故事像隐喻纠缠在一起。然后在这里实际上剧情，也就是两个人的主线跳出了这个隐喻","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"719","username":"凛凛233","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"719","dbdateline":"1544061775","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41846168","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"leolodge","authorid":"411773","dateline":"2018-12-6 10:05","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><font color=\"#999999\">wilkyway 发表于 2018-12-6 07:21</font><br />\r\n<font color=\"#999999\">片子怎么样先不论..<br />\r\nstaff那个金正恩是谁23333<br />\r\n存在感太强了</font></div><br />\n韩国代工工作室的员工啊，老熟人了，京都几部剧场版都有他","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"720","username":"leolodge","adminid":"0","groupid":"53","memberstatus":"0","number":"720","dbdateline":"1544061925","groupiconid":"11"}],"allowpostcomment":[],"comments":{"41845637":[]},"commentcount":{"41845637":null},"ppp":"30","setting_rewriterule":{"portal_topic":"topic-{name}.html","portal_article":"article-{id}-{page}.html","forum_forumdisplay":"forum-{fid}-{page}.html","forum_viewthread":"thread-{tid}-{page}-{prevpage}.html","group_group":"group-{fid}-{page}.html","home_space":"space-{user}-{value}.html","home_blog":"blog-{uid}-{blogid}.html","forum_archiver":"{action}-{value}.html","plugin":"{pluginid}-{module}.html"},"setting_rewritestatus":["portal_topic","portal_article","forum_forumdisplay","forum_viewthread","group_group","home_sp